body_html:
Hello, I've encountered this issue. I tried pip install tensorflow-tensorboard but it didn't work. This is screenshot of the files in the logdir. I'm not sure if its an issue or i'm doing something wrong but the same code worked (showed embedding no metadata) then nothing.

Here is the text from projector_config.pbtxt:
(I tried editing the slashes but no luck)
model_checkpoint_path: "C:\tmp\Tensorboard\CNN\ooo\model.ckpt-4"
embeddings {
tensor_name: "cifar_embedding"
metadata_path: "C:\tmp\Tensorboard\CNN\ooo\metadata.tsv"
sprite {
image_path: "C:\tmp\Tensorboard\CNN\ooo\cifar_images.png"
single_image_dim: 32
single_image_dim: 32
}
}
Thanks in advance.

body:
Hello, I've encountered this issue. I tried pip install tensorflow-tensorboard but it didn't work. This is screenshot of the files in the logdir. I'm not sure if its an issue or i'm doing something wrong but the same code worked (showed embedding no metadata) then nothing.
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31519736/29943079-6af1b6c0-8e6e-11e7-8932-6b1fc72f28ed.png)

Here is the text from projector_config.pbtxt:
(I tried editing the slashes but no luck)
model_checkpoint_path: "C:\\tmp\\Tensorboard\\CNN\\ooo\\model.ckpt-4"
embeddings {
  tensor_name: "cifar_embedding"
  metadata_path: "C:\\tmp\\Tensorboard\\CNN\\ooo\\metadata.tsv"
  sprite {
    image_path: "C:\\tmp\\Tensorboard\\CNN\\ooo\\cifar_images.png"
    single_image_dim: 32
    single_image_dim: 32
  }
}
Thanks in advance.
